Welcome

My name is Ryan Schmid, a computer science Master's student at Lehigh Univeristy. Before my time as a graduate student, I completed two Bachelor's degrees at Lehigh, one in Computer Engineering and the other in Inegrated Business and Engineering (IBE) with a major in Finance as part of the university's IBE Honors Program. This website is a virtual resume that displays many of the experiences I have had at Lehigh as well as some projects and achievements I have done and made along the way.
